00:36:50.680 --> 00:36:52.472
side of things, including
maybe with color.

00:36:52.472 --> 00:36:53.721
COLE NUSSBAUMER KNAFLIC: Yeah.

00:36:53.721 --> 00:36:55.650
And color is the place
that comes to my mind

00:36:55.650 --> 00:36:57.550
immediately with that question.

00:36:57.550 --> 00:37:00.810
Because one thing to be
aware of, color in particular

00:37:00.810 --> 00:37:04.930
has this unique ability
to impart tone and sort

00:37:04.930 --> 00:37:06.460
of incite emotions.

00:37:06.460 --> 00:37:08.460
And so you always want
to think about how you're

00:37:08.460 --> 00:37:10.430
using color and
what sort of tone

00:37:10.430 --> 00:37:12.300
you want to set,
whether it's in a graph

00:37:12.300 --> 00:37:15.870
or in the broader communication
that contains that graph,

00:37:15.870 --> 00:37:18.829
and use color to reinforce that.

00:37:18.829 --> 00:37:20.620
But on that note, one
thing to keep in mind

00:37:20.620 --> 00:37:22.940
is that different cultures
associate different meanings

00:37:22.940 --> 00:37:24.190
with different colors.

00:37:24.190 --> 00:37:25.752
So depending on who
your audience is,

00:37:25.752 --> 00:37:27.210
who you're
communicating to, that's

00:37:27.210 --> 00:37:28.910
something to take into account.

00:37:28.910 --> 00:37:32.820
David McCandless has its
beautiful sort of visualization

00:37:32.820 --> 00:37:34.920
that's at the same time
an interesting tool

00:37:34.920 --> 00:37:36.260
for visualizing data.

00:37:36.260 --> 00:37:38.010
It's called Colours and Culture.

00:37:38.010 --> 00:37:39.970
And it's this big color wheel.

00:37:39.970 --> 00:37:41.770
And "Colours" in
that case is British.

00:37:41.770 --> 00:37:42.480
He's British.

00:37:42.480 --> 00:37:45.720
C-O-L-O-U-R-S.

00:37:45.720 --> 00:37:47.530
But it shows you
the connotations

00:37:47.530 --> 00:37:50.330
that different colors have
in different cultures.

00:37:50.330 --> 00:37:53.950
So it can be a very useful
tool if you are communicating

00:37:53.950 --> 00:37:56.070
to an international audience.

00:37:56.070 --> 00:37:59.360
His site is
informationisbeautiful.net.

00:37:59.360 --> 00:38:00.310
