00:42:38.250 --> 00:42:40.390
on that graph so that
your audience isn't

00:42:40.390 --> 00:42:42.480
left guessing what they're
meant to get out of it,

00:42:42.480 --> 00:42:45.160
but rather you've put
that work there for them.

