much bigger, how much smaller,

00:45:29.618 --> 00:45:34.236
answer some of the more
specific questions.

00:45:34.236 --> 00:45:36.610
Whereas his view is a pie
chart absolutely has its place.

00:45:36.610 --> 00:45:38.970
It is the most effective
visual for communicating

00:45:38.970 --> 00:45:41.510
a part of a whole.

00:45:41.510 --> 00:45:44.860
But people often
misuse them and use

00:45:44.860 --> 00:45:47.910
them to try to do other
things outside of that.

00:45:47.910 --> 00:45:50.320
So his view is, rather than
banish them completely,

00:45:50.320 --> 00:45:53.840
let's teach people how
to use them smartly.

00:45:53.840 --> 00:45:54.550
I disagree.

00:45:54.550 --> 00:45:57.010
But we've agreed to disagree,
and we're on good terms.

00:45:57.010 --> 00:45:57.800
